messages.content: I cannot provide a complete list of prohibited events without more information.  To avoid issues, please review our community guidelines. If you have questions after reviewing them, please contact customer service.
I'm an organiser. What events can i not create?

To ensure your event is approved, please avoid creating events that promote hate speech, illegal activities, or misinformation.  For a complete list of prohibited events and detailed guidelines, please refer to our help center.
